OL,5,Cconfessions
OL,7,FA former Iranian prisoner has warned a
OL,8,FBritish couple who have been detained
OL,9,Fin Iran on espionage charges to "not
OL,10,Fsubmit to making false confessions".
OL,12,FCraig and Lindsay Foreman were on a
OL,13,Fmotorcycle journey around the world
OL,14,Fwhen they were detained in the Middle
OL,15,FEastern country in January.
OL,17,FAnoosheh Ashoori, 71, who was jailed
OL,18,Ffor nearly five years in Iran on
OL,19,Fspying charges, said his heart goes
OL,20,Fout to the couple and told them to
OL,21,Fremain strong.
