OL,7,FThe father-of-two, from Lewisham,
OL,8,Fsouth-east London, was arrested in
OL,9,FAugust 2017 while visiting his elderly
OL,10,Fmother in Tehran.
OL,12,FHe was convicted of allegedly spying
OL,13,Ffor Israel's Mossad intelligence
OL,14,Fagency, despite having lived in the UK
OL,15,Ffor 20 years.
OL,17,FMr Ashoori was released with fellow
OL,18,FBritish-Iranian dual national Nazanin
OL,19,FZaghari-Ratcliffe, who was also
OL,20,Fdetained on espionage charges, in
OL,21,FApril 2022.
