OL,7,F"My heart and my mind is with Craig
OL,8,Fand Lindsay and with their families in
OL,9,FBritain," Mr Ashoori told the PA news
OL,10,Fagency.
OL,12,F"I know that they have advised people
OL,13,Fnot to go to Iran, but because Iran is
OL,14,Fa beautiful country and the people are
OL,15,Fvery hospitable the temptation is
OL,16,Falmost irresistible.
OL,18,F"It's just a trap, it is not worth
OL,19,Ftaking the risk."
