OL,7,FMr Ashoori, who was kept in solitary
OL,8,Fconfinement in Evin Prison and
OL,9,Finterrogated during the first four
OL,10,Fmonths, said it was good the couple
OL,11,Fhave made their case public from the
OL,12,Fbeginning.
OL,14,F"Because they are already made public,
OL,15,Fand now there is a social awareness,
OL,16,Fthe Iranian regime will think twice
OL,17,Fabout maltreating them.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
