OL,7,F"After going through what I went
OL,8,Fthrough for two years, after taking
OL,9,Fthe foreign minister's advice not to
OL,10,Fgo public, hopefully they will not go
OL,11,Fthrough that pain."
OL,13,FMr Ashoori, who still suffers
OL,14,Fflashbacks from his ordeal, attempted
OL,15,Fsuicide three times and went on a 17-
OL,16,Fday hunger strike while serving his
OL,17,Fminimum 10-year sentence.
