OL,7,FHis and Mrs Zaghari-Ratcliffe's
OL,8,Frelease came after the UK Government
OL,9,Fagreed to pay a #400 million debt to
OL,10,FIran dating back to the 1970s.
OL,12,F"I guess maybe the main reason for
OL,13,Ftheir arrest is either money or it is
OL,14,Fa prisoner exchange," he said.
OL,16,F"Unfortunately, I think that in many
OL,17,Fcases, like these political
OL,18,Frelationships, and, for example, trade
OL,19,Fopportunities, these things come first
OL,20,Fand human rights usually come second."
