OL,7,FMr Ashoori said western countries need
OL,8,Fto unite to "confront this extortion
OL,9,Fand this hostage-taking".
OL,11,FMr and Mrs Foreman were heading for
OL,12,FAustralia, having crossed into Iran
OL,13,Ffrom Armenia on December 30, according
OL,14,Fto social media posts.
OL,16,FOn Instagram, Mrs Foreman acknowledged
OL,17,Fthat travelling to Iran, against
OL,18,FForeign Office advice, was "slightly
OL,19,Fscary".
