OL,7,FShe added: "Yes, we're aware of the
OL,8,Frisks. But we also know the rewards of
OL,9,Fmeeting incredible people, hearing
OL,10,Ftheir stories, and seeing the
OL,11,Fbreathtaking landscapes of these
OL,12,Fregions could far outweigh the fear.
OL,14,F"From the vast deserts of Iran to the
OL,15,Ftowering peaks of Pakistan, we hope to
OL,16,Fshare the beauty, hospitality, and
OL,17,Fhumanity that often go unnoticed."
