OL,7,FMrs Foreman was said to be carrying
OL,8,Fout a research project as part of the
OL,9,Fjourney, asking people what
OL,10,Fconstitutes a "good life".
OL,12,FShe was to present her findings at a
OL,13,Fconference on positive psychology in
OL,14,FBrisbane in July, it was reported
OL,15,Fearlier this month by the BBC.
