OL,7,FAn FCDO spokesman said: "We are deeply
OL,8,Fconcerned by reports that two British
OL,9,Fnationals have been charged with
OL,10,Fespionage in Iran. We continue to
OL,11,Fraise this case directly with the
OL,12,FIranian authorities.
OL,14,F"We are providing them with consular
OL,15,Fassistance and remain in close contact
OL,16,Fwith their family members."
OL,18,FThe Foreign Office advises against all
OL,19,Ftravel to Iran.
